#	(AWS GPU) g++5.4, Linux vm-shell1.doc.ic.ac.uk 4.4.0-47-generic #68-Ubuntu SMP Wed Oct 26 19:39:52 UTC 2016 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux
